document_data.mainbody:
anthleene was an inhabitant of Myth Drannor in the 3 century DR.
On , Nanthleene was at the Alastrarra manor when Elminster Aumar first came to Myth Drannor. After they decided to let him go and have the Coronal judge him, per the head of the house, Nanthee gawked at the human a little too much.
